Phillipson, Wahlert &amp; Lowry. 
<emphasis bold="true" box="[709,727,1906,1925]" pageId="2" pageNumber="203">A.</emphasis>
Flowering
</taxonomicName>
branch; 
<emphasis bold="true" box="[894,911,1906,1925]" pageId="2" pageNumber="203">B.</emphasis>
Leaf, abaxial surface; 
<emphasis bold="true" box="[1107,1124,1906,1925]" pageId="2" pageNumber="203">C.</emphasis>
Flower. [
<emphasis box="[202,420,1931,1950]" italics="true" pageId="2" pageNumber="203">Service Forestier 22132,</emphasis>
P] [Drawn by R. L. Andriamiarisoa]
